l capital group llc private company information  bloomberg july    am et capital markets company overview of rock hill capital group llc snapshot people company overview rock hill capital group llc is a private equity firm specializing in investments in recapitalizations management buyouts growth initiatives financial restructuring private family owned companies troubled companies that are in need of capital restructuring or other financial reengineering the firm does not consider investments in operational or management turnarounds it seeks to invest in small growing small to lower middle market companies it seeks to invest in industrial products and services energy services business services and valueadded distribution sectors it prefers to invest in the companies based in gulf coast and southern united states including the southeast regi rock hill capital group llc is a private equity firm specializing in investments in recapitalizations management buyouts growth initiatives financial restructuring private family owned companies troubled companies that are in need of capital restructuring or other financial reengineering the firm does not consider investments in operational or management turnarounds it seeks to invest in small growing small to lower middle market companies it seeks to invest in industrial products and services energy services business services and valueadded distribution sectors it prefers to invest in the companies based in gulf coast and southern united states including the southeast regions the firm seeks to invest in companies with an enterprise value of less than  million and having ebitda between  million and  million it makes majority and control investments rock hill capital group llc was founded in  and is based in houston texas detailed description  buffalo speedwaysuite houston tx united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwrockhillcapcom key executives for rock hill capital group llc mr randall b hale cpa founder and managing director age